---
const productiveImg = '/imgs/illustration-stay-productive.png';
const iconArrow = '/imgs/icon-arrow.svg';
---

<section class="productive">
    <img src={productiveImg} alt="Graphic image">
    <h3>Stay productive, wherever you are</h3>
    <p>Never let location be an issue when accessing your files. Fylo has you covered for all of your file storage needs.</p>
    <br />
    <p>Securely share files and folders with friends, family and colleagues for live collaboration. No email attachments required.</p>
    <span class="cta">
        <a href="https://www.frontendmentor.io/profile/SinisaVukmirovic">See how Fylo works <img src={iconArrow} alt="Icon"></a>
    </span>
</section>

<style>
    .productive {
        padding: 7rem 2rem;

        & h3 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin: 2rem 0 1rem;

        }

        & p {
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        & .cta {
            display: inline-block;
            color: var(--Cyan-cta);
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: .2rem 0;

            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--Cyan-cta);
            width: fit-content;
            cursor: pointer;

            & a {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                font-size: .8rem;
            }

            & img {
                display: inline-block;
                margin-left: .5rem;
            }
        }
    }
</style>